    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for a practical option. The exterior shows typical signs of use, including some minor scratches and paint chips consistent with its age, though there is no major structural damage. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits some wear on the upholstery and plastic trims. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it may soon benefit from routine maintenance and minor suspension work to ensure continued longevity. It's a solid, honest car that offers good value for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character.",
