    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered every single day. It looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in flawless shape, this is the one. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
