      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts its original deep-gloss paint with a professional ceramic coating and zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather still carries its factory scent, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting every fluid change and inspection. There are no scratches, no dings, and no wear on the upholstery bolsters. This car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014smooth, tight, and powerful. For the collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
